moduleName: Google People / Contact Groups / Batch Get
description: Get a list of contact groups owned by the authenticated user by specifying a list of contact group resource names.

schema.description: OAuth 2 access token. Most APIs require `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/contacts` scope. Google Auth / Service Account Token can be used to obtain a valid access token.
API key can be generated in Google Developer Console in APIs & Services section. Leave blank if OAuth access token is used.
Selector specifying which fields to include in a partial response.

Optional. A field mask to restrict which fields on the group are returned. Defaults to `metadata`, `groupType`, `memberCount`, and `name` if not set or set to empty. Valid fields are: * clientData * groupType * memberCount * metadata * name
Optional. Specifies the maximum number of members to return for each group. Defaults to 0 if not set, which will return zero members.
Required. The resource names of the contact groups to get. There is a maximum of 200 resource names.
